WEBVTT

00:01.740 --> 00:04.047
Khalil: Usually when you
hear people talk about

00:04.091 --> 00:10.053
being paid for basketball,
first thing you think is NBA.

00:10.097 --> 00:15.711
But we're here in Mexico...

00:15.754 --> 00:18.757
playing in tournaments
for money.

00:18.801 --> 00:21.021
César: Americans don't
really know what they're in for.

00:22.413 --> 00:25.068
This is mercenary basketball.

00:25.112 --> 00:28.071
♪ I spend all my time trying
to get them in, baby ♪

00:28.115 --> 00:29.420
♪ Gonna live
and make a killing, baby ♪

00:29.464 --> 00:31.379
♪ Like I was a sin, baby

00:31.422 --> 00:32.902
♪ Whoo!

00:32.945 --> 00:35.557
It ain't gonna be your
ordinary basketball game.

00:35.600 --> 00:37.472
[ Whistle blows ]Man: It's real fast --

00:37.515 --> 00:39.909
concrete, sun hitting your face.

00:39.952 --> 00:43.217
-Real physical, dirty.
-Black eyes.

00:43.260 --> 00:46.524
Put some ice on it. Both
fingers tighten up. Let's go.

00:46.568 --> 00:48.048
Is this what you came to see?

00:48.091 --> 00:49.745
♪ Whoo, whoo, whoo,
whoo, whoo, whoo ♪

00:53.096 --> 00:55.011
[ Laughter ]

00:55.055 --> 00:57.274
Man: I don't want to really say
where the money comes from.

00:57.318 --> 00:58.971
I don't want nobody
looking for me or whatever,

00:59.015 --> 01:01.670
but you almost can put it
together where it come from,

01:01.713 --> 01:05.978
'cause it's a hell
of a lot of money.

01:06.022 --> 01:07.719
César: Corruption is involved.

01:07.763 --> 01:08.894
♪ I'm not to be...with

01:08.938 --> 01:12.246
And it could be narcos, cartel.

01:12.289 --> 01:14.161
-So, you got to deal with it...
-Y'all call this

01:14.204 --> 01:16.946
a fucking game, man?
-...and play through it.

01:16.989 --> 01:19.601
It doesn't matter how you win,
it's all about the money.

01:19.644 --> 01:22.038
But I came here to pursue
my dreams of becoming

01:22.082 --> 01:23.474
a professional
basketball player.

01:23.518 --> 01:25.085
Rashad: This is your last shot.

01:25.128 --> 01:27.391
♪ I'm not to be...with,
I'm not be...with ♪

01:27.435 --> 01:31.178
♪♪

01:31.221 --> 01:33.789
Viewer discretion is advised.
I do say "nigga" a lot,

01:33.832 --> 01:36.444
so if you can't take that,
don't watch the show.

01:42.232 --> 01:49.457
♪♪

01:49.500 --> 01:56.725
♪♪

01:56.768 --> 02:01.121
César: Here in Mexico,
we love basketball.

02:01.164 --> 02:03.166
There's actually
a pro basketball league.

02:03.210 --> 02:04.907
It's called the LNBP --

02:04.950 --> 02:07.170
Liga Nacional
de Baloncesto Profesional.

02:07.214 --> 02:09.825
Announcer: Guevara with
the shot -- 3. Oh, baby!

02:09.868 --> 02:13.307
That is just exactly what
they need to go all the way!

02:13.350 --> 02:15.483
Unbelievable.

02:15.526 --> 02:18.834
But there's, like, a small
world, underground world,

02:18.877 --> 02:20.705
of tournaments
all over the country.

02:20.749 --> 02:22.359
They're not pro players.

02:22.403 --> 02:25.319
They're just, you know,
playing for the prize money.

02:25.362 --> 02:28.583
But there's some recruiters
from the pro basketball league,

02:28.626 --> 02:31.325
so Americans come to play
in the tournaments

02:31.368 --> 02:35.155
'cause they know they have
a really good chance to go pro.

02:35.198 --> 02:36.373
I'm a sponsor.

02:36.417 --> 02:38.549
I'm originally from here.

02:38.593 --> 02:40.812
I just love basketball, and, uh,

02:40.856 --> 02:43.424
I got involved
with American players.

02:43.467 --> 02:46.818
I don't know them,
so I'm gonna take the chance,

02:46.862 --> 02:49.647
but it's a different world, man.

02:49.691 --> 03:01.398
♪♪

03:01.442 --> 03:13.193
