or something.

10:35.722 --> 10:37.332
I tell you, it's gonna
be country as hell.

10:37.375 --> 10:39.508
[ Laughs ]
I'm telling you.

10:39.551 --> 10:41.118
So take it all in, man.

10:41.162 --> 10:51.172
